headline.print_headline: Keselowski Wins NASCAR Nationwide Race in Iowa
headline.main: Keselowski Wins NASCAR Nationwide Race in Iowa

lead_paragraph: Brad Keselowski held off the charging Michael McDowell on Saturday night to win the NASCAR Nationwide race at Iowa Speedway.
